MATCH (s:School {‘서울신중초등학교’}) WITH s.POLYGON as poly CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, poly) YIELD node
WITH node MATCH (node:Apartment)
RETURN node.name

MATCH (d:dong {name:'양재2동’}) WITH d CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, d) YIELD node
WITH node MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 85 AND node.size< 95 RETURN count(node)

MATCH (d:dong {name:'방배2동’}) WITH d CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, d) YIELD node
WITH node MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 30 AND node.size< 40 RETURN count(node)

MATCH (d:dong {name:'반포4동’}) WITH d CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, d) YIELD node
WITH node MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 70 AND node.size< 80 RETURN count(node)

A: 현재 5평대 매물이 제일 많은 동을 1개 보여줘
B:
MATCH (d:dong)
UNWIND d.POLYGON as p
CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, p) YIELD node
MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 0 AND node.size< 10
RETURN p.name, size(collect(node.name)) AS c ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 1

CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, p) YIELD node
MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 10 AND node.size< 20
RETURN p.name, size(collect(node.name)) AS c ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 21

MATCH (d:dong)
UNWIND d.POLYGON as p
CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, p) YIELD node
MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 20 AND node.size< 30
RETURN p.name, size(collect(node.name)) AS c ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 23

MATCH (d:dong)
UNWIND d.POLYGON as p
CALL spatial.intersects(‘POI’, p) YIELD node
MATCH (node:Apartment) WHERE node.size> 60 AND node.size< 70
RETURN p.name, size(collect(node.name)) AS c ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 30

A: 평균 소득이 가장 높은 아파트는 어디야
B:
MATCH (a:Apartment)-[:SALE]-(p)
WITH a, avg(p.income) as income
RETURN a.name ORDER BY income DESC LIMIT 1
